Diane Linkletter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diane_Linkletter 0 Diane Linkletter (October 31, 1948 – October 4, 1969) was the daughter and youngest child of popular American media personality Art Linkletter, and his wife Lois Foerster. She was 20 years old when she committed suicide in 1969.
